title: Morgantown Mayhem (2004)
description:
This documentary contains explicit language, violence, and brief nudity.

Soundtrack featuring 6'6 240, The Whiskey Dicks, Tony G-run-G, Big Chief, 304 Reconz, Nauseous, Meuwl, D.O.Ceasar, Ace Beanz, E2 Entertainment, and Sound Vizion Recordings

"Journey into the mountains of West Virginia and discover Morgantown. This city is host to some of the most mayhem filled parties ever. This documentary will put you right in the middle of the mayhem with an all access V.I.P pass to the hottest parties, from gameday tailgates to derby days. Loaded with the best couch burning, beer guzzling, shot slamming, knee slapping, ass stomping, bitch fighting, cleavage exposing, cop macing, tobacco chewing video clips this side of the Monongahela River.

Loaded with a Mayhem filled soundtrack featuring Morgantown's best musical acts from 304 Reconz to The Whiskey Dicks. Strap on your beer goggles and grab your favorite sheep cause you're invited to the mountains for this mayhem filled jamboree!

This documentary is not supported or affiliated with WVU."

2004 Pig Productions
